.  See also  Rupert ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"When Robert D'Anvers was born in 1225, in Tetsworth, Oxfordshire, England, United Kingdom, his father, William d'Anvers II, was 29 and his mother, Matilda de Talemasche, was 25. He married Petronilla Freeman in 1250, in Tetsworth, Oxfordshire, England. They were the parents of at least 4 sons and 3 daughters. He died in 1274, in his hometown, at the age of 49."},"et":{"1225–1274":"1225–1274","1252–1282":"1252–1282","1252–Male":"1252–Surnud","1254–Male":"1254–Surnud","1256–1281":"1256–1281","1256–1331":"1256–1331","1256–Female":"1256–Surnud","1258–Female":"1258–Surnud","1197–1246":"1197–1246","1201–1250":"1201–1250","abt 1250":"1250","1274":"1274","1197":"1197","1252":"1252","Abt 1258":"umbes 1258","Bef 1246":"enne 1246","1250":"1250","1282":"1282","1281":"1281","Abt 1252":"umbes 1252","1225":"1225","1258":"1258","Abt 1256":"umbes 1256","1246":"1246","1256":"1256","1201":"1201","Abt 1254":"umbes 1254","1222":"1222","1331":"1331","1254":"1254","Tetsworth, Oxfordshire, England, United Kingdom":"Tetsworth, Oxfordshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Oxfordshire, England, United Kingdom":"Oxfordshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Tetsworth, Oxfordshire, England":"Tetsworth, Oxfordshire, England","Berkshire, England, United Kingdom":"Berkshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1225–1274":"1225–1274","1252–1282":"1252–1282","1252–Male":"1252–Kuollut","1254–Male":"1254–Kuollut","1256–1281":"1256–1281","1256–1331":"1256–1331","1256–Female":"1256–Kuollut","1258–Female":"1258–Kuollut","1197–1246":"1197–1246","1201–1250":"1201–1250","abt 1250":"1250","1274":"1274","1197":"1197","1252":"1252","Abt 1258":"noin 1258","Bef 1246":"ennen vuotta 1246","1250":"1250","1282":"1282","1281":"1281","Abt 1252":"noin 1252","1225":"1225","1258":"1258","Abt 1256":"noin 1256","1246":"1246","1256":"1256","1201":"1201","Abt 1254":"noin 1254","1222":"1222","1331":"1331","1254":"1254","Tetsworth, Oxfordshire, England, United Kingdom":"Tetsworth, O